\id 1PE - Tabo (Aramia dialect) NT - Papua New Guinea 2006 (DBL 2014) 
\h 1 Pit 
\toc3 1 Pit 
\toc1 Pitakono Dopo Leta Ebete Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰tamo Ododiyaęž‰ 
\toc2 1 Pita 
\mt1 PITAKONO DOPO LETA  
\mt2 EBETE HIBIMAęž‰ MIDIPAęž‰TAMO ODODIYAęž‰  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Na baęž‰ Pitatela, Yaęž‰su Kelisote ebeno sose tupuimimaęž‰ hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hopamo doelamiyaęž‰, baęž‰bi okopi ipuwalo na baęž‰ etala.  
\p Godote ebeno tawakalubimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamaęž‰ pui kaęž‰kaęž‰lamiholiyaęž‰, ibi ipuwalo komo laęž‰ Yudiya hopone hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hopamo ikuliti baęž‰bo daęž‰nemedehonama, baęž‰ma kaęž‰na komo laęž‰ Pontase hopolo, komo Galesiya hopolo, komo Kaęž‰padosiya hopolo, komo Aęž‰isiya hopolo, baęž‰gala komo Bitiniya hopolo, laęž‰le baęž‰moi hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hopolo bemedehonamata, nale baęž‰moe leta laęž‰ hiliyonomatamo baęž‰bemaęž‰ poememo.  
\v 2 Baęž‰ hibila, yaęž‰lo tetelo Nabiwi Godote laęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰lamiyaęž‰ta laęž‰le ebeno Gobogoboeno heloamo ebeno talona tawakalubimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamaęž‰, iyo, ebete ubi bihatiyaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisokono hawaęž‰mo laęž‰eno tepo ipuwoeno dalowaęž‰ ukulalelamete, laęž‰le ebetamo hibilo kopapamilaęž‰halenamaęž‰.  
\p Wadiyala Godokono malemale komo baęž‰gala hete komote laęž‰godolo konomamo naęž‰polaęž‰namenaęž‰.   
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Hido Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Haba Lawemaęž‰ Yaęž‰sukunu Pe Tete Daęž‰latimina  
\p
\v 3 Wadiyala a kalakala tabo aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono Nabiwitamo kadipatemaęž‰nemaęž‰, mabu ebe baęž‰ hibi Godola. Numaęž‰laęž‰, ebete ebeno konomo malemale baęž‰ma kaęž‰na hawakalimiyaęž‰, ebete Yaęž‰su Kelisoko hoe ipuwane kaęž‰kaęž‰mo dadipatiyaęž‰ baęž‰be komodo uli kaęž‰kaęž‰ atamo ikaaęž‰miyaęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ale ebeno pe komomaęž‰ uliholo kalakalago ebe belatiminamaęž‰,  
\v 4 mabu baęž‰ba tetelo Godote ebeno gugudi mabumaęž‰ daęž‰hiduilamiyaęž‰ ale baęž‰bi hidohido ilina hibilo kuwatemaęž‰nemaęž‰. Baęž‰bi hidohido ilinate ebeno Hunu Habalo ba polaęž‰na emedena tetelo aęž‰kawibohonamenaęž‰ baęž‰gala aęž‰kababalehonamenaęž‰ baęž‰gala aęž‰kakubakubahanamenaęž‰.   
\p
\v 5 Baęž‰ hibila, Godoko ubila ebete baęž‰moe hopoeno Kuititi Hegelalo ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo laęž‰tamo ikalame, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebete laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komodo ebeno heloamo laęž‰ nitaguaęž‰midalenata.  
\v 6 Baęž‰moe mabumaęž‰ laęž‰ naęž‰kalakalahanalaęž‰, iyo, hibila, baęž‰ma tetelo laęž‰le komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ temeteme ipuwalo ba emedena menemene iyaęž‰tawahanakomata, huiyatiya tete tatalila laęž‰eno kalakala tete kopuluhukumaęž‰ne.   
\p
\v 7 Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moe hopolo iyaęž‰tawahapaęž‰te golodo ilina koe ipuwamo dihatemenaęž‰, koete golodo ilinoeno dalowaęž‰ ba upulaęž‰ ibaęž‰te baęž‰be ilinoeno hido aęž‰laęž‰mina komo baęž‰bo kumimaęž‰naęž‰. Baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na Godote laęž‰eno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ temeteme ipuwalo ebeno hido oko bowatina laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komo kulamelelamemaęž‰, daęž‰ hibilaęž‰ o daęž‰ hibihaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, hopo habanapaęž‰te golodo ilina duminaka hidonomomaęž‰ gaęž‰lanaka, mabu tete nanekelelo baęž‰be hopo ilinoeno aęž‰laęž‰mina komote konomamo kitanamaęž‰ne. Huiyatiya kalakala konomola, laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komoeno hido komote baęž‰bako golodo ilinoeno hido komo naęž‰gogolona, mabu hibimaęž‰ midi komote laęž‰godolo emedena tetelo aęž‰kawibonamene. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ temeteme ipuwalo kodakodalo naęž‰laęž‰motaęž‰hanalaęž‰, mabu Yaęž‰su Kelisote gala daęž‰kapemene, ebete laęž‰ ba pimililamehole laęž‰ pawagaminalete hunamo baęž‰bo kopewadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelemaęž‰naęž‰ta.  
\v 8 Laęž‰le ebe dopamo kuminakuihaęž‰ baęž‰gala baęž‰ma tetelo laęž‰eno baidaęž‰mo ebe kuminahaęž‰, huiyatiya laęž‰le ebe hibimaęž‰ ba midina malemalelo baęž‰bo emalagidolonamata. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ laęž‰eno temeteme koamo emalagidoleheno konomo kalakalate laęž‰godolo bitana, baęž‰bako kalakala bada konomolaęž‰kaęž‰! Iyo, tawakalubaęž‰te baęž‰bako kalakala tabamo hawakalimi modobohaęž‰!  
\v 9 Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰be kalakalate laęž‰godolo hibilo bitana, mabu laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komodo laęž‰le Godogodone kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo naęž‰lawenamata.   
\p
\v 10 Dopamo tetelo Godokono ukui hawakalimipaęž‰te baęž‰moe kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komoeno hibi komo kiyaęž‰tawahamaęž‰ ebeno Bukoeno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tabo komokomo bekaęž‰lamiholenakuyaęž‰, baęž‰bene ibaęž‰te baęž‰ma kaęž‰na gaęž‰lanakuyaęž‰, galane tetelo Godote ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰tamo malemalelo dito kikalamemaęž‰naęž‰ta.  
\v 11 Huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, ibaęž‰te baęž‰moe eta komo nipo umiyaęž‰, Godokono kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komote keba kaęž‰na naęž‰kaęž‰pemene baęž‰gala kebako tetelo naęž‰kaęž‰puluhukumini. Baęž‰ba tetelo Kelisokono Gobogobote ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komoeno pe tete ibaęž‰tamo hibilo kahawakalimiyaęž‰haęž‰, huiyatiya ebete ibi ipuwado baęž‰ma kaęž‰na olamaginakui, Godokono Oemedawa Kelisote daęž‰pemene, ebete dopamo koko temeteme uwatete, galane Godote ebeno hido aęž‰laęž‰mina komamo ebe baęž‰bo kawagaminamaęž‰ne.  
\v 12 Baęž‰gala ibino oko owati ipuwalo Godote ibi aęž‰kiyalamiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te kebe komokomo daęž‰gaęž‰lanakui baęž‰bi komate ibaęž‰tamo aęž‰kikulihamenaęž‰ huiyatiya galane tawakalubaęž‰tamo kikulihomaęž‰naęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ baęž‰ baęž‰bi tawakalubilata, iyo, laęž‰ tetelo komo Godokono okopaęž‰te pikuliti Yaęž‰sukunu Hido Tabo ebeno Hunu Haboeno Talona Gobogoboeno heloamo laęž‰tamo aęž‰polamagiminakuyaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, Hunu Haboeno nopopaęž‰te ibino ubi konomamo miyaęž‰tena, laęž‰le kebe ugumuili komo kuwatiuyaęž‰ma, ibaęž‰te baęž‰bi hidohido komo atumu kakiyaęž‰tawahamaęž‰.   
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Godokono Talona Ipuwalo Emedeho Komo  
\p
\v 13 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰le Godokono hido oko kowatihonamaęž‰ laęž‰eno ukui naęž‰hiduilamaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰gala wadiyala laęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisokono pe komomaęž‰ uliholo nemedehonalaęž‰, mabu ebete daęž‰pehawakalamene baęž‰be hegelalo ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo laęž‰tamo malemalelo kopikalamemaęž‰naęž‰ta.  
\v 14 Baęž‰gala dopamo tetelo laęž‰le Godokono hibi komo iyaęž‰tawahaheno kebe komo kododilinakuima, laęž‰ baęž‰ma tetelo ebegodone ohobilaęž‰hate baęž‰bi kateneno ubi komokomo ododili komodo hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰pimo gala akemedehonalaęž‰.  
\v 15 Huiyatiya laęž‰ Godotamo ba papamilaęž‰ha ebeno tutumu tabo hiliyonomo ipuwalo eta kapiya adikanaleheno, wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno hiliyonomo ododili komo ipuwalo talonamaęž‰ nedaęž‰huyaęž‰laęž‰. Iyo, laęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰lamiyaęž‰la baęž‰be Kodawate talonamaęž‰ keba kaęž‰na kedaęž‰na laęž‰ baęž‰ atumu baęž‰ba kaęž‰na nemedehonalaęž‰,  
\v 16 mabu ebete ebeno Bukalo a baęž‰ma kaęž‰na iyaęž‰tuaęž‰mena, â€śLaęž‰eno ododili komo ipuwalo talonamaęž‰ nedaęž‰hanalaęž‰, mabu na baęž‰ Talonanomolo Emededawala.â€ť   
\p
\v 17 Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godote kapiya tuputupunomo gabodo hiliyonomo hopo habanapino komokomo kanagilamelelamemaęž‰ne, iyo, ebe baęž‰ hido huiya baęž‰gala kuba huiya ibaęž‰tamo modobolo dikalamemene baęž‰be Kodawala, baęž‰gala hibila, laęž‰le ebetamo daęž‰toetoehonakoma ebe laęž‰eno Nabiwimaęž‰ kaęž‰minakomata. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰moe hopolo kapelapimo ba emedehona, laęž‰eno ododili ipuwalo ebe tolemelo ebe kapiyatamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanakuyaęž‰laęž‰,  
\v 18 mabu laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala laęž‰eno hido huiyate ebegodone kopemaęž‰ne, baęž‰gala laęž‰le dopamo iniwalaęž‰godone daęž‰lawiyaęž‰ma baęž‰be emede komoeno ododili ipuwalo ebeno hibi kaęž‰kaęž‰ komo nipo umiyaęž‰mata. Iyo, dopamo laęž‰le baęž‰be pakala emede komamo daęž‰papamilaęž‰hanamima Saitanakono du genamanapimaęž‰ ba edaęž‰hana, Godote laęž‰ malemalelatelelo baęž‰be du genama ipuwane baęž‰bo uluhukulateliyaęž‰ta. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ebete laęž‰ baęž‰moe hopoeno manaęž‰mo kuwatiyaęž‰haęž‰,  
\v 19 huiyatiya ebete laęž‰ Kelisokono huiya konomo hawaęž‰mo laęž‰ aęž‰huiyaliyaęž‰ta. Iyo, eta kuba kapiyate Kelisogodolo itanaheno, ebete hidonomo sipi-goe dehaęž‰poto huiyamaęž‰ ba edaęž‰na laęž‰eno kuba ododili mabumaęž‰ ebeno ape hawaęž‰goeno malemale ilinamaęž‰ miditi Godotamo baęž‰bo ikamiyaęž‰.  
\v 20 Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰moe hopo ododihino dopamo Godote Kelisoko yaęž‰lo aęž‰kaęž‰miyaęž‰ laęž‰eno kaęž‰kaęž‰ komulaęž‰lelamemaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ kalakala konomola, a tetelo baęž‰moe hopoeno kuititi tete ba tatali ebete hopo habanapaęž‰tamo baęž‰bo pehawakaluyaęž‰,  
\v 21 baęž‰bene ebete daęž‰hoiyaęž‰ baęž‰ba tetelo Godote hoe ipuwane ebe ba adipate ebeno helonomo alago ebe baęž‰bo awagaminuyaęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ laęž‰le Kelisoko ipuwado Godoko hibimaęž‰ ba midina, ebegodone laęž‰eno hidohido komo hibilo uwatemaęž‰ ebeno pe komo uliholo latiminamata.   
\p
\v 22 Numaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ Godokono hibi komamo ba papamilaęž‰ha laęž‰eno tepo ipuwa ukulaliyaęž‰mata laęž‰le laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midipi ekaki malemalelo hibilo kemalagidolenamaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ ipuwalo etate eta kemalagidolo, etate eta kemalagidolo, laęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na ba ewagelena laęž‰eno tepo ipuwoeno konomo malemalaęž‰mo komopi nemalagidolenalaęž‰.  
\v 23 Baęž‰ hibila, dopamo laęž‰eno nabi baęž‰ puyaęž‰te ibino kadele tetaęž‰mo nikuliti daęž‰nehaęž‰lahuyaęž‰ ibi baęž‰ baęž‰bi dubula, huiyatiya baęž‰ma tetelo laęž‰ baęž‰ Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Nabiwi Godokono gugudilata, iyo, laęž‰le ebeno wibohaęž‰ Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Tabodo hawakalahalete uliulinomaęž‰ edaęž‰huyaęž‰mata.  
\v 24 Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ Godokono Bukalo tabote baęž‰ma kaęž‰na itana,  
\b  
\q1 â€śTawakalubi hiliyonomo baęž‰ hemo keba kaęž‰nalaęž‰kaęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰nala,  
\q2 baęž‰gala ibino awagaha komokomo  
\q2 baęž‰ haiyaino titi huiyala.  
\q1 Kaęž‰lo dapepehuta baęž‰bi hemate dumutu hegelalo kowaiwaihomaęž‰naęž‰,  
\q2 baęž‰gala kaęž‰lo hido titaęž‰gopi daęž‰polaęž‰na  
\q2 baęž‰bi haiyaaęž‰te dumutu hopamo dito komaęž‰tilaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰.   
\q1
\v 25 Godokono Tabote huiyatiya  
\q2 emedena emedena tetelo bitanamene.â€ť  
\b  
\m Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moe tabo baęž‰ komopaęž‰te dopamo tetelo laęž‰tamo dolamagimiyaęž‰ baęž‰be Hido Tabola.   
\c 2  
\s1 Yaęž‰suku Baęž‰ Godokono Genamoeno Nakola Huiya Hototola  
\p
\v 1 Baęž‰moe baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ laęž‰godolo daęž‰polaęž‰na baęž‰bi hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kuba hiliyonomo tamaęž‰mo naęž‰miyaęž‰taęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰ma kaęž‰na haęž‰da tabo akolamagiminakalaęž‰, baęž‰gala maęž‰lapila netewa komo naęž‰miyaęž‰palaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰gala komopino ilinamaęž‰ akamaubahalenakalaęž‰, baęž‰gala tawakalubino mahilo kubahilame talonala.  
\v 2 Laęž‰ huiyatiya aęž‰liaęž‰li gugudimo ba edaęž‰ha Godokono Gobogoboeno hido nono nihomaęž‰ laęž‰ laęž‰eno ubi komo konomamo nihatenalaęž‰, iyo, baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na laęž‰ laęž‰eno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo hibilo lawemaęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo kapepehomaęž‰nemata.  
\v 3 Baęž‰ hibila, dopamo tetelo laęž‰ Kodawoeno malemale totomaęž‰namidate golanomomaęž‰ baęž‰bo gaęž‰luyaęž‰mata.   
\p
\v 4 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰le Ko Kaęž‰kaęž‰dawa Yaęž‰sutamo naęž‰pelamaęž‰laęž‰, ebe baęž‰ tawakalubaęž‰te kubamaęž‰ gaęž‰late tamaęž‰mo dihatiyaęž‰ baęž‰be dawala, huiyatiya Godote ebe hidonomo nakola huiya hototomaęž‰ goelo baęž‰bo lawiyaęž‰.  
\v 5 Numaęž‰laęž‰, ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰te laęž‰ ipuwalo atumu baęž‰ka-itana, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ pelamete laęž‰ haęž‰kiya laęž‰ Godotamo naęž‰pikamehalaęž‰, laęž‰le ebe adikumino genamoeno hidohido kehamaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamaęž‰. Baęž‰bene laęž‰ baęž‰be genama gulu ebe ba owatidolona ebeno Gobogoboeno talona oko owati komodo malemale ilina ebetamo ikamehopimaęž‰ bedaęž‰hanamata, baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰le Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ipuwado ebetamo dikamehonakoma, ebete kalakalago laęž‰godone buwatenakomene.  
\v 6 Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godote baęž‰be komo hawakalimimaęž‰ ebeno Bukalo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na goena,  
\b  
\q1 â€śNa hidonomo nakola huiya abo lawete  
\q2 Yelusalema ko habalo\f * \fr 2.6 \ft Buka kaęž‰lamiholedawa, wadiyala amaęž‰ niyaęž‰tawa, Yelusalema haboeno eta mahilo baęž‰ Sayonola.\f* detenamo  
\q2 baęž‰be genamoeno hototomaęž‰ komidimaęž‰nemo.  
\q1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ kebe lumagiti baęž‰be dawa hibimaęž‰ daęž‰midimini,  
\q2 ebete emedena tetelo hilopo komo aęž‰kiyaęž‰tawanamene.â€ť   
\b  
\p
\v 7 Baęž‰ hibila, laęž‰ puyaęž‰te Yaęž‰suku hibimaęž‰ daęž‰midinama, laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala ebe baęž‰ Godokono huiya konomo hototomaęž‰ edaęž‰na. Huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, komopaęž‰te ebe hibimaęž‰ kamidinahaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ Godokono Buka tabote ibino ubihaęž‰ komo hawakalimimaęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na goena,  
\b  
\q1 â€śGenama etepaęž‰te tamaęž‰mo dihati,  
\q2 baęž‰be hototote huiyatiya genamoeno helo mabumaęž‰ edaęž‰na.â€ť   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Baęž‰gala Godokono Bukalo eta tabote baęž‰ma kaęž‰na itana,  
\b  
\q1 â€śBaęž‰moe Kodawa baęž‰ gabo tetelo ditana baęž‰be nakolala,  
\q2 tawakalubaęž‰te ibino kuba ubi komago ba tolame  
\q1 ebegodolo nato nukamidahalete  
\q2 ebe hunamo baęž‰bo konegudimaęž‰naęž‰.â€ť  
\b  
\p Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibila, ibaęž‰te Godokono tabo hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰ mabumaęž‰ nato ukamidahalete baęž‰bo gudinaka, Godote ibi mabumaęž‰ yaęž‰lo daęž‰goiyaęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na.   
\b  
\p
\v 9 Huiyatiya laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipino komo hiyaęž‰nomola. Laęž‰ baęž‰ Godote ebeno ubilo duwatiyaęž‰la baęž‰bi tawakalubilata, baęž‰gala laęž‰ Ko Gawadubu Godoko adikumilo ebetamo malemale ilina dikamehonakoma, laęž‰ baęž‰ baęž‰bi okopilata. Iyo, laęž‰ baęž‰ ebetamo talona oko dowatinama baęž‰bi kapiyuimipilata, baęž‰gala laęž‰ baęž‰ Godokono hiyaęž‰nomo tawakalubimaęž‰ edaęž‰hanamata. Baęž‰ hibila, Godote laęž‰ du ipuwane aęž‰kaęž‰lamiyaęž‰ta, mabu ebe ubila laęž‰le ebeno hidonomo alo ipuwalo ba emedena ebeno hidohido ododili komokomo komopaęž‰tamo kolamagiminakomaęž‰.  
\v 10 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ kalakala konomola, laęž‰le dopamo tetelo Godokono tawakalubimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamihaęž‰ huiyatiya kaęž‰lo laęž‰ baęž‰ ebeno gugudilata, baęž‰gala dopamo laęž‰ ebeno malemale kiyaęž‰tawahuyaęž‰haęž‰ huiyatiya baęž‰ma tetelo ebegodone aęž‰lawiyaęž‰mata.   
\s1 Godoko Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Baęž‰moe Hopolo Kapelapimaęž‰ Dedaęž‰hana Baęž‰be Komo  
\p
\v 11 Naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, nale laęž‰ betoelameholemata laęž‰ baęž‰moe hopolo ba emedehona kapelapimaęž‰ nedaęž‰hanalaęž‰, mabu laęž‰ baęž‰ Godokono Hunu Habanapilata. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰eno kateneno ubi komamo akapapamilaęž‰halaęž‰, mabu baęž‰bi kuba ubi komate laęž‰eno gobogoboeno kaęž‰kaęž‰go ba alaholoho laęž‰ kubahilamemaęž‰ ewagelena.  
\v 12 Baęž‰gala laęž‰le hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰go ba emedena ibino holoholo hapulu hidohido komo kapiya nododilinakuyaęž‰laęž‰, mabu ibi ipuwalo puyaęž‰te laęž‰ kubapimaęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰lamina, ibaęž‰te laęž‰eno hidohido ododili komo ba ulamena laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ ukui hiyaęž‰maęž‰ baęž‰bo komidilimaęž‰naęž‰. Iyo, hibila, Godote hopo habanapino komo anagilamelelamemaęž‰ daęž‰pemene, baęž‰be Ko Hegelalo baęž‰bi atu tawakalubaęž‰te laęž‰eno hidohido ododili komomaęž‰ Godokono mahilo kadipatemaęž‰naęž‰.   
\s1 Gabomani Okopaęž‰tamo Papamilaęž‰ha Komo  
\p
\v 13-14 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Kodawa Yaęž‰suku mabumaęž‰ laęž‰le Loma habanapino Konomo Gawadubutamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanalaęž‰, mabu hopo konomolo ebeno helote hibilo bitana. Baęž‰gala ebete komo hiliyonomo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hopamo daęž‰noelamiyaęž‰ baęž‰bi koko gawadubu baęž‰gala ibino komo gabomani okopi, wadiyala laęž‰ ibi hiliyonomatamo atumu naęž‰kapapamilaęž‰halenakuyaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰bi dubagodolo helo bitana kuba ododilipaęž‰tamo kuba huiya ba ikalame hidohido komo ododilipi hunamo kowadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelemaęž‰naęž‰.  
\v 15 Baęž‰moe mabumaęž‰ Godokono ubi komo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na bitana, keba tetelo ebeno hibi komo iyaęž‰tawahaęž‰paęž‰te laęž‰ kubapimaęž‰ daęž‰kaęž‰lamiminaęž‰, laęž‰le laęž‰eno hidohido ododili komamo ibino daedae tabo gaęž‰la komo baęž‰bo koduhilamemaęž‰nemata.  
\v 16 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ Kelisoko ipuwalo tutupimaęž‰ dedaęž‰hanama, laęž‰ hidamo! Laęž‰ daedae ukuilo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na akagaęž‰lalaęž‰, â€śKelisote aeno kuba huiya yaęž‰lo uwateaęž‰miyaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ale aeno kuba ubi komokomo gala daęž‰kododilimaęž‰, Godogodone kuba huiya aęž‰kalawaęž‰maęž‰.â€ť Ao, eba kaęž‰nahaęž‰! Wadiyala laęž‰ huiyatiya laęž‰eno ape Godotamo ikamehonomo nikamehuyaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰le laęž‰eno ododili ipuwalo ebeno huiyahaęž‰ okopimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamaęž‰.  
\v 17 Baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na laęž‰le komo hibimaęž‰ midipi hiliyonomo malemalelo ba emalagidole Godoko kapiya naęž‰tolemenalaęž‰. Baęž‰gala baęž‰moe hopo konomolo helomaęž‰ dedaęž‰na, baęž‰be Lomanapino Konomo Gawadubuino komomaęž‰ laęž‰le laęž‰eno tepo ipuwalo kuba tabo gaęž‰laheno ebeno tutumamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanakuyaęž‰laęž‰. Iyo, wadiyala laęž‰ haęž‰kiya laęž‰ hopamo ba miyaęž‰te, komo tawakalubi hiliyonomoeno komomaęž‰ laęž‰eno tepo ipuwoeno ukuilo ibi hunamo naęž‰wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelenakuyaęž‰laęž‰.   
\s1 Oko Namutulubaęž‰tamo Papamilaęž‰ha Komo  
\p
\v 18 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ koko oko dubate laęž‰ pui manaęž‰mo duwatiyaęž‰la, wadiyala laęž‰le baęž‰bi dubuino huiyahaęž‰ oko kowatihonamaęž‰ laęž‰eno tepo ipuwalo ibino komomaęž‰ kuba tabo gaęž‰laheno ibaęž‰tamo oko helonomamo nowatinakuyaęž‰laęž‰. Iyo, oko namutulubi ipuwalo puyaęž‰te laęž‰ daęž‰malemalelatelena, laęž‰le hidohido oko ibi kapiyatamo owatihoheno, puyaęž‰te laęž‰ kiyahalamelo laęž‰tamo daęž‰maubahalena, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰bako oko namutulubaęž‰tamo atumu kalakalago naęž‰papamilaęž‰halenakuyaęž‰laęž‰.  
\v 19 Baęž‰ hibila, amaęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na ba ewagelena amiaęž‰no kuba ododihaęž‰ tetelo etate amaęž‰tamo temeteme dikamemenaęž‰, Godote baęž‰be komo umiti amaęž‰tamo kokalakalamaęž‰ne mabu amaęž‰ amiaęž‰no tepo kodakoduimilo ebeno ubi komamo naęž‰papamiwatanata.  
\v 20 Huiyatiya amaęž‰ oko kubamo owati ipuwalo namutudawate hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ temeteme amaęž‰tamo dikamehomenaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo amaęž‰ amiaęž‰no tepo kodakoduimilo ko komohaęž‰maęž‰ daęž‰goemenaęž‰, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ Godote amaęž‰tamo baęž‰kaęž‰kalakalamene? Ao, ebeno kalakalate aęž‰kitanamene mabu amaęž‰ baęž‰ kuba okodawalata, huiyatiya keba tetelo amaęž‰ hido oko owati ipuwalo temeteme daęž‰lawemenaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ebeno kalakalate amaęž‰tamo hibilo kitanamaęž‰ne.   
\s1 Yaęž‰suti Ebeno Hoe Ipuwalo Koko Temeteme Duwatiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 21 Baęž‰ hibila, Godote laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi aęž‰kaęž‰lamiyaęž‰ta, laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi mabumaęž‰ baęž‰moe hopoeno temeteme ipuwalo kopolaęž‰namaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Kelisote laęž‰eno kaęž‰kaęž‰ komulaęž‰lelamemaęž‰ ebeno hoe ipuwalo koko temeteme keba kaęž‰na kuwatiyaęž‰, Godoko ubila laęž‰ Kelisokono nato bobodo ebe hibilo kotaęž‰matanamaęž‰.  
\v 22 Iyo, numaęž‰laęž‰, Kelisote eta kuba kododiyaęž‰haęž‰ baęž‰gala ebegodolo eta haęž‰da amiho komo puliyala.  
\v 23 Baęž‰gala kubapaęž‰te ebe diduduputimiyaęž‰ ebete huiyatiya ibaęž‰tamo iduduputilame tabamo kahuiyuyaęž‰haęž‰, iyo, ebete ibaęž‰godone koko temeteme duwatiyaęž‰, ebete ibi kiyahalamelo ibaęž‰tamo kuba huiya ikalamemaęž‰ kagoiyaęž‰haęž‰. Baęž‰ba tetelo ebete huiyatiya ebeno hibimaęž‰ midi komo Godotamo ihatiyaęž‰ ebete ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ komulaęž‰memaęž‰, mabu ebe iyaęž‰tawuyaęž‰ galane baęž‰be Kodawate hiliyonomo tawakalubino komo tuputupunomo gabodo kanagilamelelamemaęž‰ne.  
\v 24 Baęž‰bene Kelisote haęž‰kiya ebeno apaęž‰mo aeno kuba ododili komo uwateaęž‰mete keha pihigamo baęž‰bo watuyaęž‰. Ebete baęž‰ba kaęž‰na ododiyaęž‰ mabu ebe ubila ale aeno kuba ododili ipuwalo haęž‰lahate ebeno tuputupu emede ipuwalo kemedehonamaęž‰, iyo, ebete ebeno temeteme uwate komodo laęž‰ aęž‰hiduilamiyaęž‰ta.  
\v 25 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, dopamo tetelo laęž‰ hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ dalatidiholiyaęž‰ma baęž‰bi sipi-goegoemo emedehonamimata, huiyatiya kaęž‰lo Godote laęž‰ gala aęž‰kamagaheliyaęž‰ta laęž‰eno Hido Sipi-goegoe Ulamedawa kotaęž‰matanamaęž‰, ebe baęž‰ laęž‰eno tepo ipuwoeno Ukui Buiyaęž‰minaledawala.   
\c 3  
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipi Kamenakamena Baęž‰gala Ibino Awi Ibaęž‰te Kapimilo Keba Kaęž‰na Naęž‰kemedehonamenaęž‰  
\p
\v 1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ kamenakamenalaęž‰, nale okopi ibino namutulubaęž‰tamo papamilaęž‰hamaęž‰ keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰kiyalamemo, wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰ atumu laęž‰eno awaęž‰tamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanakuyaęž‰laęž‰. Diyala, ibi ipuwalo komopaęž‰te Yaęž‰sukunu Hido Tabo hibimaęž‰ kamidinahaęž‰, huiyatiya laęž‰le ebeno Hibi Taboeno eta komo ibaęž‰tamo gaęž‰laheno, laęž‰eno hidohido ododili komate ibi hibi gabo baęž‰bo kiyaęž‰tulamemaęž‰naęž‰ ibaęž‰te atumu hibimaęž‰ midipimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hamaęž‰.  
\v 2 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰eno ododili ipuwalo eta dalowaęž‰ ukui komote itanaheno, laęž‰le Godoko laęž‰eno ukui komamo dawagaminanama, wadiyala ibaęž‰te baęž‰bi netewa komo laęž‰eno emede ipuwalo hidamo nulamenamenaęž‰.   
\p
\v 3 Baęž‰gala wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno hunu tama hiduilamemaęž‰ koamo akemalagidolonalaęž‰. Baęž‰ma kaęž‰na laęž‰eno hinibo hiduilame komo, baęž‰gala huiya kokonomo tulikahula pupuli komo, baęž‰gala galoeno nolenole pupuli komo, baęž‰gala hidohido kaliko pupuli komo, baęž‰bi komo hiliyonomo baęž‰ koko komohaęž‰.  
\v 4 Huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, ko komo baęž‰ tepo ipuwa hiduilame komola, mabu kebe kamenate ebeno tepo ipuwa daęž‰hiduimimini, baęž‰be hido komote ebegodolo aęž‰kawibamene, iyo, baęž‰bako hido tataba emede komote ebegodolo ba itana, Godote baęž‰be komo umiti hidonomomaęž‰ kogoemaęž‰ne.  
\v 5 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰le yaęž‰lo tetelo tuputupulu demedehonamaęž‰ baęž‰bi kamenakamenoeno emede komo nemalagidolalaęž‰. Ibaęž‰te Godoko hibimaęž‰ ba midina ibino awaęž‰tamo papamilaęž‰ha komodo ibi haęž‰kiya ibino tepo ipuwa hidohidonomomaęž‰ baęž‰bo midilinakuyaęž‰,  
\v 6 iyo, baęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na Selate ebeno awi Aęž‰ibalahamatamo hidonomamo papamiwatalo ebe ebeno hido namutudawamaęž‰ kaęž‰minakui. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰le Selako ba ibamitina laęž‰eno awi tolelameheno ibaęž‰tamo hidohido komo dododilinakoma, laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo laęž‰ baęž‰ ebeno bohelemele gugudimaęž‰ bedaęž‰hanamata.   
\p
\v 7 Baęž‰gala hibimaęž‰ midipi dubalaęž‰, laęž‰ atumu laęž‰eno kamenakamenago tatabalo ba emedehona hido ukuiaęž‰go ibi nowalubilinakuyaęž‰laęž‰, mabu laęž‰eno helote ibino helo naęž‰gogolona. Iyo, wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno tepo ipuwoeno ukuilo laęž‰ haęž‰kiya laęž‰ hopamo ba miyaęž‰te laęž‰eno kamenakamena hunamo naęž‰wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelenakuyaęž‰laęž‰, mabu Godote tawakalubaęž‰tamo malemalelo dikalamena ibaęž‰te baęž‰be wibohaęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰ laęž‰go kapimilo kolawemaęž‰naęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na dewagelema, Godote laęž‰eno toetoe tabo ulihomaęž‰ eta komote gigiho aęž‰kakalapilamene.   
\s1 Hidohido Ododili Komokomo Mabumaęž‰ Temeteme Lawe Komo  
\p
\v 8 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipino emede komomaęž‰, na Pitate kuititi tabo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na goemo. Wadiyala laęž‰ hiliyonomate ukui kapiyamaęž‰ edaęž‰hate tatabalo nemedenalaęž‰, baęž‰ma kaęž‰na awagaha komote laęž‰tamo akapaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰gala laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi malemalelo ba emalagidolena, ibino temeteme komomaęž‰ laęž‰eno tepo ipuwa akakodakoduilamaęž‰laęž‰.  
\v 9 Baęž‰bene eta lumagiti amaęž‰tamo kuba dododimini, amaęž‰ ebeno kubamaęž‰ akahuiyalaęž‰, baęž‰gala ebete amaęž‰tamo mela tabo daęž‰goemene, amaęž‰ ebeno mela tabo huiyaheno huiyatiya ebe mabumaęž‰ Godoko naęž‰kiyamiyaęž‰ ebete ebe hidamo kowalubinamaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, Godote ebeno malemale amaęž‰ ipuwado hawakalimimaęž‰ amaęž‰ yaęž‰lo aęž‰kaęž‰miyaęž‰ta, mabu baęž‰be gabodo ebeno hido owalubi komote amaęž‰tamo atumu baęž‰kapenakomene.  
\v 10 Baęž‰moe baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ Godokono Bukalo tabote baęž‰ma kaęž‰na itana,  
\b  
\q1 â€śKebe lumagiti kalakalago emedemaęž‰ ubi dihatemene,  
\q2 ebete kubakuba tabo baęž‰gala haęž‰da amiho tabo akolamaginakalaęž‰.   
\q1
\v 11 Baęž‰gala wadiyala ebete kuba ododili ipuwane ohobigate  
\q2 hidohido komo nododilinakamene,  
\q1 iyo, ebete ebeno ubi konomamo nihatenakamene  
\q2 komopi hiliyonomago tatabalo kemedenamaęž‰.   
\q1
\v 12 Baęž‰ hibila, puyaęž‰te baęž‰ba kaęž‰na tuputupupimaęž‰ dedaęž‰hana,  
\q2 Kodawa Godote ibi hidonomamo ba ulamena  
\q2 ibino toetoe tabo ulihonako,  
\q1 huiyatiya puyaęž‰te kuba komokomo dododilina,  
\q2 ebete ibaęž‰tamo alaholo komo bododinako.â€ť   
\b  
\p
\v 13 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ amaęž‰le hidohido komo ododilimaęž‰ helonomomaęž‰ dedaęž‰menaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo eta lumagiti ubi aęž‰kihataęž‰mene amaęž‰ kubahimimaęž‰.  
\v 14 Huiyatiya diyala, eta tetelo amaęž‰ hido komo ba ododi komopaęž‰te temeteme amaęž‰tamo daęž‰ ikametamenaęž‰, baęž‰bene baęž‰be temeteme ipuwalo ibaęž‰tamo akatoletolaęž‰laęž‰ baęž‰gala aka-ukuibilibilaęž‰laęž‰, huiyatiya amaęž‰ koamo naęž‰kalakaluyaęž‰!  
\v 15 Iyo, amaęž‰ amiaęž‰no tepo ipuwalo Kelisoko kapiya tolemelo ebe hunamo ba adipate Kodawamaęž‰ naęž‰kaęž‰minakuyaęž‰, baęž‰gala wadiyala amaęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na naęž‰hidonakuyaęž‰, keba tetelo Kelisoko iyaęž‰tawahaęž‰ lumagiti amiaęž‰no hibimaęž‰ midi komomaęž‰ amaęž‰ daęž‰kiyamemenaęž‰, amaęž‰ baęž‰be komoeno ipuwa ebe hidamo baęž‰bo kiyaęž‰tumimaęž‰naęž‰ta.  
\v 16 Baęž‰bene amaęž‰ amiaęž‰no komo ebetamo daęž‰hawakalimiminaęž‰, wadiyala amaęž‰ haęž‰kiya amaęž‰ hopamo ihatelo amiaęž‰no ukuiaęž‰mo ebe ba adipate tataba gabodo ebe nowalubiyaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, amaęž‰le amiaęž‰no ododili ipuwalo Kelisokono tuputupudawamaęž‰ ba edaęž‰na amiaęž‰no tepo ipuwoeno mulu ukui komamo daęž‰papamiwatanakomenaęž‰, puyaęž‰te amiaęž‰no Kelisoko taęž‰mata mabumaęž‰ amaęž‰ iduduputimilo kuba tabo dolamagimina, galane ibaęž‰te amiaęž‰no hido emede komo ba emalagidolo hilopo baęž‰bo kolawemaęž‰naęž‰.  
\v 17 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibimaęž‰ mididawa, amaęž‰ numaęž‰. Godote ubi dihatemene, amaęž‰le eta hido ododi komo mabumaęž‰ temeteme daęž‰lawemenaęž‰, kubahaęž‰, baęž‰ hido komola, mabu baęž‰bako temeteme ipuwalo Godokono kalakalate amaęž‰tamo kitanamaęž‰ne, huiyatiya keba tetelo amaęž‰ kuba ododi ipuwalo temeteme daęž‰lawemenaęž‰ ebete amaęž‰tamo aęž‰kakalakalamene.   
\s1 Yaęž‰sukunu Koko Temeteme Komodo Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰ Komo Daęž‰lawiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 18 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ Kelisokono komo nemalagidolalaęž‰. Ebe baęž‰ tuputupudawanomola, huiyatiya ebete hopo habanapino kuba ododili hiliyonomo mabumaęž‰ koko temeteme uwatete baęž‰bo hoiyaęž‰, baęž‰moe gabodo ebete a Godotamo aęž‰magahiyaęž‰ ale ebeno hidohido mabulubimaęž‰ kedaęž‰hanamaęž‰. Numaęž‰laęž‰, tawakalubaęž‰te Yaęž‰suku danakapumiyaęž‰ baęž‰ba tetelo ebeno katene apeno kaęž‰kaęž‰te dito wibuyaęž‰, huiyatiya Godote hoe ipuwane ebe dadipatiyaęž‰ ebete wibohaęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰ ape baęž‰bo kalawiyaęž‰, iyo, ebete emedena emedena tetelo gala aęž‰kahoenamene.  
\v 19 Baęž‰gala baęž‰moe baęž‰ eta komola. Godote ebe kaęž‰kaęž‰mo adipateheno dopamo Yaęž‰suti Saitanakono du genama guamo tote Godokono tabo baęž‰bo nolamagiyaęž‰.  
\v 20 Baęž‰bolo puyaęž‰te ebeno tabo dulihuyaęž‰, ibi baęž‰ hopo habalo Godotamo papamilaęž‰hahaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰hanamaęž‰ baęž‰bi kuba ododilipino haęž‰laha gobogobola, iyo, Nowate konomo boge dododiyaęž‰ Godote hido tete ibaęž‰tamo baęž‰bo ikalamiyaęž‰, huiyatiya ibaęž‰te ebeno tabo kulihuyaęž‰haęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ hulama beyate dodoluyaęž‰ baęž‰ba tetelo hopo habanapi ipuwalo kapiyakapiyate Nowakono boge guamo nogomuyaęž‰, iyo, aęž‰iti tawakalubinomate beya ipuwane ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo ba lawe komo hiliyonomate baęž‰ dito haęž‰lahuyaęž‰. \fig Nowakono konomo bogela|alt="Ark floating, a few mountains" src="CO00630B.TIF" size="span" loc="1/3 of page in middle" copy="1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="3.20" \fig*   
\p
\v 21 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Nowako tetelo duluhukuyaęž‰ baęž‰be hulama beya baęž‰ go komola. Iyo, kaęž‰lo hibimaęž‰ midipino beyamo wadulatele komo baęž‰ ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ gabola, huiyatiya baęž‰be ododi ipuwalo beyate lumagino tepo ipuwa aęž‰kukulamaęž‰mene, ao, beyate hunu tamoeno dalowaęž‰ kapiya kukulamaęž‰ne. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo keba kaęž‰nalaęž‰kaęž‰? Lumagiti beyamo aduti komo lawe tetelo ebeno tepo ipuwoeno mulu ukui komamo papamiwatalo Godotamo hibilo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na daęž‰goemene, ebete ebeno emede ipuwalo tuputupu komokomo kapiya kododilinamaęž‰, baęž‰be komodo ebete kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo kolawemaęž‰ne, mabu Yaęž‰su Kelisote ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ baęž‰bako lumagitamo ikamemaęž‰ hoe ipuwane gala aęž‰kamahiguyaęž‰.  
\v 22 Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰be Kaęž‰kaęž‰dawoeno helo konomola. Ebete Hunu Habamo gala kanodolote baęž‰bolo Godokono tu hapuamo daęž‰nemediyaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetene tupuimiti baęž‰ma tetaęž‰mo puluhuku hiliyonomo nopopaęž‰te, Godokono nopopi baęž‰gala Saitanakono nopopi, helohelonomo nopopi baęž‰gala helohelodopo nopopi, ibi hiliyonomate Yaęž‰sukunu ubi komamo baęž‰papamilaęž‰halenakomenaęž‰.   
\c 4  
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Kuba Ododili Komone Godotamo Ohobilaęž‰ Komo  
\p
\v 1 Baęž‰ hibila, Kelisote baęž‰moe hopolo ba emedena ebeno apaęž‰mo koko temeteme iyaęž‰tawanakui, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno temeteme ipuwalo ebeno hido owalubi ukui atumu kodakodalo naęž‰lawiyaęž‰laęž‰, alaholodawate ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰maęž‰ gili kibili keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰lawenako baęž‰ba kaęž‰na. Numaęž‰laęž‰, pote ebeno hibimaęž‰ midi mabumaęž‰ ebeno apaęž‰mo temeteme duwatenako, baęž‰be lumagiti pakala emede komoeno kuba ododili komamo gala aęž‰kapapamiwatanakamene,  
\v 2 iyo, ebete ebeno hoe kuititaęž‰mo ba nuluhuku Godokono ubi komamo baęž‰papamiwatanakomene, ebeno kateneno ubi komamohaęž‰.   
\p
\v 3 Baęž‰ hibila, hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te kebe kuba komokomo dododilinaka, laęž‰ komo gogo hiliyonomolo baęž‰bi atu komo beka-ododilinakuimata. Iyo, dopamo laęž‰ laęž‰eno kateneno ubi komamo ba papamilaęž‰hale bohelemele pilo komo, baęž‰gala gamoda niho ipuwalo daedaemaęž‰ edaęž‰ha komo, baęž‰gala hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hilopo poko ipuwalo emedeho komo, baęž‰moi komate laęž‰ ipuwalo kokonomomaęž‰ edaęž‰hanamaęž‰, baęž‰gala laęž‰ Godokono eta ko tutumu tabo adikanalete idaęž‰daęž‰li badikulamenamimata. Huiyatiya kalakala konomola, laęž‰ baęž‰bi kuba ododili komokomo aęž‰miyaęž‰paliyaęž‰mata,  
\v 4 iyo, baęž‰ma tetelo laęž‰le hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰go baęž‰bako koko kuba baęž‰gala daedae ukui komokomo kododilinahaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ibaęž‰te laęž‰ mabumaęž‰ konomamo laęž‰waęž‰hate laęž‰ baęž‰bo iduduputilamenakata.  
\v 5 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibila, Godokono Ko Hegelalo ibaęž‰te ebeno holoholo hapulu daęž‰nutitatamenaęž‰, ebete ibino hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kuba ododili mabumaęž‰ ibaęž‰tamo huiya ba ikalame ebe duhimimaęž‰ ibaęž‰te eta tabo gaęž‰lamaęž‰ aęž‰kamodobamenaęž‰. Iyo, baęž‰be Helodawate yaęž‰lo hidote bemedena, baęž‰moe hopolo dopamo demedehonamaęž‰ baęž‰gala kaęž‰lo tetelo demedehona baęž‰bi tawakalubi hiliyonomoeno ododili komokomo anagilamelelamete ibaęž‰tamo modobo huiya kikalamemaęž‰ne.  
\v 6 Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moe baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ Yaęž‰sukunu Hido Tabote haęž‰lahapaęž‰tamo duluhukuyaęž‰. Iyo, baęž‰baęž‰te hopo habalo ba emedehona ibino apaęž‰mo dododilinakui baęž‰bi kuba mabumaęž‰ Godote ibaęž‰tamo hoe huiya ikalamete, baęž‰bene ebete ebeno ubi komo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ihatiyaęž‰, baęž‰bi haęž‰lahapino gobogobate Hido Tabo uliho ipuwalo uli kaęž‰kaęž‰ uwatete Godokono ubi komamo emedena emedena tetelo baęž‰papamilaęž‰hanakomenaęž‰.   
\s1 Godote Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰tamo Hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ Helo Dikalamiyaęž‰ Ibaęž‰te Ebeno Oko Kowatihonamaęž‰  
\p
\v 7 Numaęž‰laęž‰, tete tatalila baęž‰moe hopoeno hiliyonomo komokomate kowibohomaęž‰naęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ tepo kodakoduilamete baęž‰be komote pemaęž‰ uliholo nemedeniyaęž‰laęž‰, mabu baęž‰moe gabodo laęž‰ Godotamo toetoe tabo olamagimi ipuwalo helonomomaęž‰ kedaęž‰hamaęž‰nemata.  
\v 8 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰eno hiliyonomo ododili komokomo ipuwalo baęž‰moe komo baęž‰ ko komonomola. Wadiyala laęž‰eno emede ipuwalo etate eta malemalelo nemalagidolonalaęž‰, mabu keba tetelo laęž‰ malemale ipuwalo demedenama, baęž‰ba tetelo etate etoeno kuba ododili komokomo koamo emalagidolemeheno tiyolo kegebolememaęž‰nemata.  
\v 9 Baęž‰gala wadiyala laęž‰ ubihaęž‰ tabo gaęž‰laheno komopaęž‰te komopi baaęž‰mo baęž‰gala laha haboeno komamo nowalubihuinakuyaęž‰laęž‰.   
\p
\v 10 Baęž‰gala baęž‰moe baęž‰ eta komola. Godote malemalelo hibimaęž‰ midipi hiliyonomatamo ebeno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ helo ikalamiyaęž‰ ibaęž‰te ebeno oko kowatihonamaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibimaęž‰ mididawa, ebete amaęž‰tamo kebe hiyaęž‰nomo helo dikamiyaęž‰la, wadiyala amaęž‰ baęž‰be heloamo komo tawakalubi hidamo nowalubilinakuyaęž‰.  
\v 11 Baęž‰ma kaęž‰na Godote kebe lumagitamo helo dikamiyaęž‰ ebeno tabo kolamaginamaęž‰, wadiyala ebete hibilo nolamaginakamene, baęž‰gala Godote potamo helo dikamiyaęž‰ komopino modobohaęž‰ komokomo ipuwalo ibi kowalubilinamaęž‰, wadiyala ebete baęž‰be heloamo baęž‰bako tawakalubi hidonomamo nowalubilinakamene. Baęž‰moe baęž‰be gabodo laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipino hiliyonomo ododili ipuwalo komopaęž‰te Yaęž‰su Kelisokono mahilo ba adipate Godoko baęž‰bo kawagaminamaęž‰naęž‰.  
\p Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala konomo awagaha komo baęž‰gala konomo helo komote Kelisogodolo emedena emedena tetelo naęž‰polaęž‰namenaęž‰! Baęž‰moe tabo baęž‰ hibinomola, baęž‰baęž‰la!   
\s1 Yaęž‰suku Taęž‰matapaęž‰te Temeteme Ipuwalo Emede Komo  
\p
\v 12 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ temeteme ipuwalo demedehonama akalaęž‰waęž‰halaęž‰, mabu temeteme komate Godokono tawakalubaęž‰tamo daęž‰pikulinaka baęž‰be komo baęž‰ uli komohaęž‰.  
\v 13 Iyo, laęž‰eno temeteme ipuwalo wadiyala laęž‰ naęž‰kalakalahalaęž‰, mabu laęž‰le kebako hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ temeteme duwatenakoma Kelisote dopamo baęž‰bako atu temeteme aęž‰ka-uwatenakui. Baęž‰ hibila, galane ebete ebeno helonomo alago daęž‰pehawakalamene, baęž‰ba tetelo laęž‰ konomamo kokalakalahamaęž‰nemata.  
\v 14 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ komopaęž‰te baęž‰ma tetelo laęž‰eno Kelisoko taęž‰mata mabumaęž‰ laęž‰ diduduputilamemenaęž‰, laęž‰ naęž‰kalakalahuyaęž‰laęž‰ mabu ibino iduduputilame komote baęž‰moe komo behawakalimina, Godokono aęž‰laęž‰mina Gobogobote laęž‰ ipuwalo hido oko bowatina.   
\p
\v 15 Baęž‰ hibila, eta lumagiti eta lumagi dito danakapumimini, baęž‰gala etate etoeno ilina pilolo daęž‰lawemene, baęž‰gala etate gabomanino eta tutumu dadikanalemene, baęž‰gala etate ebeno pataęž‰ ipuwalo komopaęž‰tamo menemene dito dikalamemene, wadiyala baęž‰bako kuba ododi lumagiti huiya ba lawe temeteme niyaęž‰tawamene. Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godoko ubihinola laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi ipuwalo etate baęž‰bako kuba ododi komodo temeteme huiya lawe,  
\v 16 huiyatiya hibimaęž‰ mididawate Kelisoko taęž‰mata mabumaęž‰ temeteme daęž‰lawemene, baęž‰be komo baęž‰ hido komola, ebe akahilopalaęž‰. Iyo, lumagiti Kelisokono mahilo mabumaęž‰ temeteme ipuwalo daęž‰lutamene, wadiyala ebete kalakala Godotamo hunamo nadipataęž‰mene!   
\p
\v 17 Baęž‰ hibila, hopo habanapino komokomo anagilamelelame tete baęž‰ aęž‰pe. Baęž‰ba tetelo Godote a hibimaęž‰ midipino ododili komo dopamo anagilameleaęž‰mete atamo modobo huiya kikaaęž‰memaęž‰ne, baęž‰bene galane ebete ebeno Hido Tabo hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰pino kuba ododili komokomo ba anagilamelelame huiya konomo ibaęž‰tamo atumu baęž‰bo kakikalamemaęž‰ne. Baęž‰ba tetelo ibino temeteme bada konomolaęž‰kaęž‰!  
\v 18 Baęž‰moe mabumaęž‰ Godokono Bukalo tabote baęž‰ma kaęž‰na itana,  
\b  
\q1 â€śTuputupudawate ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo  
\q2 lawemaęž‰ kodakodadopola,  
\q1 baęž‰bemaęž‰ puyaęž‰te Godotamo papamilaęž‰ha ubihaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰hana,  
\q2 baęž‰gala puyaęž‰te kuba komokomo dododilina,  
\q1 ibaęž‰te kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo keba kaęž‰na naęž‰kaęž‰lawemenaęž‰?  
\q2 Gabote aęž‰kitanamene, puliyanomola!â€ť   
\b  
\p
\v 19 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ puyaęž‰te Godokono ubilo temeteme ipuwalo demedehonama, wadiyala laęž‰ tuputupu komokomo ba ododili laęž‰ haęž‰kiya laęž‰eno kaęž‰kaęž‰ Godotamo hibilo nikamehonakuyaęž‰laęž‰. Ebe baęž‰ laęž‰ hidonomamo dododiliyaęž‰la baęž‰be Helodawala, baęž‰gala ebete laęž‰ kowalubilimaęž‰ kebe komo ododimaęž‰ dopamo daęž‰goiyaęž‰, galane ebete baęž‰be komo hibinomolo kododimaęž‰ne.   
\c 5  
\s1 Sose Watowatopaęž‰te Ibino Sipi-goegoe Hidamo Ulame Komo  
\p
\v 1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ na Pitate, laęž‰ puyaęž‰te laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midipino kapiyuimi ipuwalo watowatopimaęž‰ dedaęž‰hanama, na ubila laęž‰ eta tabo kokiyalamemaęž‰, mabu na baęž‰ atumu sose watodawa etala. Baęž‰ hibila, Kelisote temeteme duwatiyaęž‰ nale naeno baidaęž‰mo umiyaęž‰mo, baęž‰gala ebete helonomo alago daęž‰pehawakalamene baęž‰ba tetelo nale ebeno alo ipuwalo ebaęž‰go kolutamaęž‰nemo. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ nale laęž‰ sose watowatopi baęž‰ma kaęž‰na tutumulatelemata,  
\v 2 wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno tepo ipuwalo ubihaęž‰ tabo gaęž‰laheno, Godote laęž‰tamo dikalamiyaęž‰la laęž‰ laęž‰eno ubi konomamo baęž‰bi sipi-goegoe hidamo nulameniyaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰gala laęž‰eno oko owati ipuwalo oko huiya lawemaęž‰ koamo emalagidoloheno, huiyatiya laęž‰le Godokono kalakalago komo tawakalubi hiliyonomo dito nowalubilinakuyaęž‰laęž‰  
\v 3 Baęž‰gala watowatopaęž‰laęž‰, Godote laęž‰tamo dikalamiyaęž‰la laęž‰ baęž‰bi sipi-goegoe kubamo kiyahalamelo wato kokomaęž‰ akedaęž‰halaęž‰. Wadiyala laęž‰le huiyatiya laęž‰eno tataba emede komodo ibaęž‰tamo hido go ba hawakalimina ibi baęž‰ba kaęž‰na naęž‰magahelenakuyaęž‰laęž‰.  
\v 4 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na ba ewagelena, laęž‰ sipi-goegoe ulamepino Kodawate daęž‰puluhukumini, baęž‰ba tetelo koko gawadubate ibino watamo daęž‰pupulinaka laęž‰ baęž‰bako hidohido aęž‰laęž‰minale pake ilina ebegodone kuwatemaęž‰nemata. Kalakala konomola, baęž‰bi pake ilinoeno aęž‰laęž‰mina komote emedena tetelo aęž‰kawibonamene.   
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰te Komo Tutumu Tabamo Papamilaęž‰ha Komo  
\p
\v 5 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ komo hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰laęž‰, nale atu gabodo laęž‰ komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tabo kokiyahalamemaęž‰nemata. Laęž‰ uli apepeho dubalaęž‰, wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno watowatopaęž‰tamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanalaęž‰, baęž‰gala laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi hiliyonomalaęž‰, laęž‰ haęž‰kiya laęž‰ hopamo ba miyaęž‰te etapaęž‰te etapaęž‰tamo huiyahaęž‰ okopimaęž‰ nedaęž‰hanalaęž‰, mabu Godokono Bukalo tabote baęž‰ma kaęž‰na itana,  
\b  
\q1 â€śPuyaęž‰te dawagahana Godote ibaęž‰go nalaholohona,  
\q1 huiyatiya puyaęž‰te ibi haęž‰kiya ibi hopamo daęž‰miyaęž‰tena,  
\q1 ebete ibaęž‰tamo ebeno ko malemale behawakaliminako.â€ť   
\b  
\p
\v 6 Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ laęž‰ haęž‰kiya laęž‰ hegehegemaęž‰ ba midili Godotamo daęž‰papamilaęž‰halema, Godote ebeno hido tetelo laęž‰ hunamo ba wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latele kokopimaęž‰ komidilimaęž‰naęž‰ta.  
\v 7 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno ukui bilibili komo hiliyonomo ebetamo miyaęž‰palenomo naęž‰miyaęž‰palaęž‰laęž‰, mabu ebete laęž‰ malemalelo konomamo emalagidolenata.   
\p
\v 8 Laęž‰ hidamo! Laęž‰ uliholo nemedehonalaęž‰, mabu laęž‰go alaholohodawa ebe baęž‰ Saitanatela, ebe konomo layono-gaha huiyala, iyo, ebete tawakalubaęž‰tamo tole konomo ba ikalame ugahalo ibi nalemaęž‰ oholena.  
\v 9 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo kodakodalo ba laęž‰motaęž‰hana ebetamo alaholoho komo nododinakuyaęž‰laęž‰, mabu laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala ebaęž‰go alaholo ipuwalo laęž‰ kapiyate kemedenahaęž‰, iyo, baęž‰moe hopo konomolo laęž‰eno komo hibimaęž‰ midipi ekakaęž‰te baęž‰ atu temeteme ipuwalo ka-emedehona.  
\v 10 Huiyatiya kalakala konomola, laęž‰ tete nanekelelo temeteme ipuwalo emedaęž‰tepate, galane Godote haęž‰kiya laęž‰eno temeteme ipuwane laęž‰ uluhukulatelete hibilo koheluilamemaęž‰naęž‰ta, laęž‰le laęž‰eno tepo ipuwalo ukui gagagagamaęž‰ edaęž‰hakapomaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰be Konomo Malemaledawate dopamo tetelo laęž‰ Kelisoko ipuwado aęž‰kaęž‰lamiyaęž‰ta laęž‰le ebeno helonomo alago emedena tetelo kemedehonamaęž‰,  
\v 11 baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala konomo helo komote ebegodolo emedena tetelo nitanamene! Baęž‰moe tabo baęž‰ hibinomola, baęž‰baęž‰la! \fig Saitanako konomo layono-gaha huiyala|alt="Male lion" src="HK00046B.TIF" size="span" loc="1/2 of page" copy="Horace Knowles, British and Foregin Bible Society 1954, 1967, 1972" ref="5.8" \fig*   
\s1 Pitate Leta Kuititi Hapulu Tabo Komokomo Dolamagiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 12 Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moe dehaęž‰poto leta Sailasiti na mabumaęž‰ pepamo miyaęž‰teho, naeno umi ipuwalo ebe baęž‰ eta hido hibimaęž‰ mididawa ekawila. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ naeno leta kuititi hapulu laęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na kiyalamemata, nale laęž‰ laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo kowalubilimaęž‰ baęž‰moi tabo komokomo bemiyaęž‰tehomo, iyo, baęž‰bi komate Godokono hibi malemale behawakalimita, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ baęž‰be malemale ipuwalo kodakodalo naęž‰laęž‰motaęž‰hanalaęž‰.   
\p
\v 13 Numaęž‰laęž‰, nago daęž‰kapiyuiminaka baęž‰bi Baęž‰baloni\f * \fr 5.13 \ft Buka kaęž‰lamiholedawa, wadiyala amaęž‰ baęž‰moe komo niyaęž‰tawa, Loma ko habalo demedehonamaęž‰, baęž‰bi hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰te Loma habanapino konomo awagaha komo ba emalagidolo ibaęž‰te ibino haba Baęž‰baloni mahilamo kaęž‰minakuyaęž‰, mabu puyaęž‰te dopamo hibi Baęž‰baloni habalo demedehonamaęž‰ ibaęž‰te ibino konomo awagaha ipuwalo Godotamo koko kuba bododilinakuyaęž‰.\f* sose hibimaęž‰ midipino kapiyuimi baęž‰gala laęž‰eno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ sose kapiyuimi, laęž‰eno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kapiyuimi baęž‰ kapiya badininipala bohelemele huiyala, iyo, Godote ebeno ubilo laęž‰ keba kaęž‰na kuwatitiyaęž‰la, ebete baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na ibi atumu aęž‰kuwatiyaęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ibaęž‰te ibino nolata tabo bepoemaęž‰ laęž‰tamo, baęž‰gala naeno gudu Makate atumu nolata tabo bekapoeme.  
\v 14 Wadiyala laęž‰ daęž‰kapiyuimima, laęž‰ hiliyonomo etapaęž‰te etapaęž‰tamo laęž‰eno malemale kohawakalimimaęž‰ kokoto uwatehuilo naęž‰paęž‰watamehuiyaęž‰laęž‰.  
\p Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ puyaęž‰te Kelisoko ipuwalo demedehonama, ebeno kalakalate laęž‰ hiliyonomagodolo nitanamene. Baęž‰moe baęž‰ naeno tabo kuititila. Baęž‰baęž‰la.   